{
  "texts": [
    "The hardware imple-mentation of Piccolo is provided using just 4 NOR gates, 3 XOR gates, and 1 XNOR gate.",
    "The 4×4 S-box proposal provides respectable non-linearity and differential consistency.",
    "Piccolo was tested vulnerable to a biclique attack for Piccolo-10 bytes for 28 rounds.",
    "Piccolo-10bytes and Piccolo-12-bytes versions are susceptible to related-key impossible differential attacks for 14 rounds [74,75].",
    "PRESENT:The version of the PRESENT algorithm was purely based on the SPN structure, which is simple, efficient, and concerned with bit-orientation [76]."
  ]
}